A former Big Brother Naija star, Dorathy Bachor has expressed concern over the economic state of the country.  Dorathy revealed on Twitter that she is mourning over the depreciating value of the naira as the equivalent of one dollar is now 515 naira. According to the Delta State-born, she is not talking to anyone because of this as she is in grief. She wrote, “$1 = 515 Naira I’m not talking to anyone today…I’m mourning my account” $1 = 515 Naira   Source